---
import { Card } from '@/components/Card';
import { CardContainer } from '@/components/CardContainer';
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout title='FAQ'>
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

  <CardContainer className='basic-card-grid'>
    <Card className='basic-card' title='How long do the treats last?'>
      <div slot='content'>
        Our treats are best consumed within 6 months when stored in an airtight
        container at room temperature. For maximum freshness, you can store them
        in the refrigerator.
      </div>
    </Card>

    <Card className='basic-card' title='Are your treats safe for puppies?'>
      <div slot='content'>
        Yes! Our treats are made with natural ingredients and are safe for
        puppies over 12 weeks old. For training, we recommend our smaller
        training-sized treats.
      </div>
    </Card>

    <Card className='basic-card' title='What ingredients do you use?'>
      <div slot='content'>
        We use only human-grade, natural ingredients like fresh fruits,
        vegetables, and pure peanut butter. No preservatives, artificial colors,
        or flavors are ever used.
      </div>
    </Card>

    <Card className='basic-card' title='Where can I buy your treats?'>
      <div slot='content'>
        Our treats are available at local farmers markets and can be ordered
        directly. Visit our Purchase page for locations and ordering
        information.
      </div>
    </Card>

    <Card className='basic-card' title='Do you offer custom orders?'>
      <div slot='content'>
        Yes! We can accommodate custom orders for special occasions or dietary
        needs. Please contact us directly to discuss your requirements.
      </div>
    </Card>

    <Card className='basic-card' title='What size treats should I choose?'>
      <div slot='content'>
        We offer training size treats perfect for small dogs and training
        sessions, and regular size treats suitable for everyday rewards for all
        dog sizes.
      </div>
    </Card>

    <Card className='basic-card' title='Do you ship your treats?'>
      <div slot='content'>
        Yes, we offer shipping within the local area. Please contact us for
        shipping rates and availability in your area.
      </div>
    </Card>

    <Card className='basic-card' title='How many treats per day?'>
      <div slot='content'>
        Treats should make up no more than 10% of your dog's daily caloric
        intake. The appropriate number varies based on your dog's size and
        activity level.
      </div>
    </Card>
  </CardContainer>

  <div class='cta-container'>
    <p>Still have questions? We're here to help!</p>
    <a href='/contact.html' class='cta-button'>Contact Us</a>
  </div>
</ContentLayout>

<style>
  .cta-container {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
</style>
